[SN]TITLE[SN]
Lorry drivers cross bridge with wind turbine blades

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Scottish lorry drivers transporting wind turbines have been praised on social media after being filmed crossing a bridge in Dumfries and Galloway.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
5 November 2016 Last updated at 13:32 GMT
Landscape gardener Dabby McCreadie witnessed their skills as the convoy passed Bargrennan Bridge near Newton Stewart.
Dabby's video has been viewed more than 40,000 times after he posted it to his Facebook page.
